node.text: Mum’s #猪脚醋 #vinegarpigstrotter is soooo good! I need to get her recipe!
@ggluvee 👍🏻👍🏻 is this common in HK too? We normally eat this during confinement. 😂
@happyzboys Pretty much the same in HK, ppl with newborns would give it away to friends and family on the 1st month of the baby. But we can have it at yumcha restaurants even in supermarkets now!
@ggluvee same here! Instead of giving it away, we normally cook a pot for the guests who come for the 满月酒! And yes some restaurants or food stalls sell them too. 😋
Yums! Love 猪脚醋！Just had this today too! 😍😍😍
@la_f_am that’s so true!! Hope my boys will think the same too. 😂
Mom's cooking is always the best.💕💕
I need too!!! For my confinement haha
